(Mark D. Smith-USA TODAY Sports) Photos: OKC Thunder Top Denver 111-98 In Preseason Game 
Oklahoma City Thunder center Enes Kanter (11) drives to the basket against Denver Nuggets center Nikola Jokic (15) during the third quarter at Chesapeake Energy Arena in Oklahoma City on Sunday, Oct. 18, 2015. (Mark D. Smith-USA TODAY Sports) Photos: OKC Thunder Top Denver 111-98 In Preseason Game 
Oklahoma City Thunder forward Serge Ibaka (9) lies on the floor after being fouled against the Denver Nuggets during the third quarter at Chesapeake Energy Arena in Oklahoma City on Sunday, Oct. 18, 2015. (Mark D. Smith-USA TODAY Sports) Photos: OKC Thunder Top Denver 111-98 In Preseason Game 
Oklahoma City Thunder forward Kevin Durant (35) drives to the basket against Denver Nuggets forward Darrell Arthur (00) and center Nikola Jokic (15) during the fourth quarter at Chesapeake Energy Arena in Oklahoma City on Sunday, Oct. 18, 2015. (Mark D. Smith-USA TODAY Sports) Photos: OKC Thunder Top Denver 111-98 In Preseason Game 
Denver Nuggets forward Joffrey Lauvergne (77) dunks the ball against the Oklahoma City Thunder during the first quarter at Chesapeake Energy Arena in Oklahoma City on Sunday, Oct. 18, 2015. (Mark D. Smith-USA TODAY Sports) 
The Oklahoma City Thunder faced the Denver Nuggets in preseason play on Sunday night at Chesapeake Energy Arena in Oklahoma City. The Thunder won 111-98.
